c Studies at Swansea University.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aTheaterxProduction and directionzSpainzCatalonia. 4aFilm & Theatre. 4aHispanic Studies. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / Spanish & Portuguese.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBoydell and Brewer Complete eBook-Package pre 2013z978311143139040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781846159190?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781846159190423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781846159190/original  a978-3-11-143139-0  Boydell and Brewer Complete eBook-Package pre 2013b2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles